text:
Aisha Harumi Tochigi (born 1996 in Chiba, Japan) is a Japanese-Ghanaian model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Universe Japan 2020.
Pageantry.
Tochigi began her pageantry career representing Chiba in the Miss Universe Japan 2019 and finish in the Top 5 and lost to eventual winner Ako Kamo. Aisha joined again and was crowned Miss Universe Japan 2020 competition on October 29, 2020. She will represent Japan at Miss Universe 2020.
